{"tid":1295450,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑暗兵法討論】焦土派理應全面入場","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:29:49.000Z","uid":71606,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f672122efa1697ce7f11f4421f0141815087cc8","tid":1295450,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"經過琴日，大家都清楚知道警察已經集大權於一身。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">一個地方唔比有普通路人。&rarr;宵禁令，行政權。\n公開講唔洗委任證&rarr;口up即成法，立法權\n執法權&rarr;本身已有。\n叫教育局炒個通識老師、干預名校試卷&rarr;教育、考評權\n去信要求英國議員道歉&rarr;外交權\n要求醫管局交病人名、要求私隱專員公署配合&rarr;醫管及司法權</code></pre><br />\n既然如此，不如公開遊行爭取<span style=\"color: red;\">廢除特區政府</span>。成立<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警政特別管理區</span>。所有高官收入比晒警察，每人人工加一萬以上。<br />\n主打<strong>林鄭無能，步步退讓</strong>口號，<br />\n將警察先係平定香港亂局<span style=\"color: red;\">唯一</span>希望依個訊息帶到成個香港。<br />\n聚集淺藍民氣反政府而非反警察，建立起非<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>即<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span>更非<strong>勇武</strong>既第三條抗爭道路。<br />\n<br />\n各位覺得點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4d5766e7028d3d51a2b9cfa6cca30a2edafe54","tid":1295450,"uid":71606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"更甚者，可以向社會指出成立香港警政特別管理區後大可將立法司法及各司局等歸入管理。<br />\n平時廢佬最憎既<strong>政棍</strong>，抗爭者最憎既<strong>狗官</strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全部留任但減薪處理。</span><br />\n務求食晒所有<em><strong>中立</strong></em>，<em><strong>港豬</strong></em>，<em><strong>偏藍</strong></em>及<em><strong>淺藍</strong></em>既目光。"},{"pid":"12519aea4dd1f60b4a68521bacc5355485f30f81","tid":1295450,"uid":268327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgD17zw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgD17zw.png&h=0d0fa98c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295142\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295142</a><br />\n<br />\n集氣推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\